name: Mackenzie Davis
description:
Mackenzie Davis is a Canadian actress and model, known for her roles in Terminator, Black Mirror, Halt and Catch Fire and Station Eleven, among others.

Update! I've realised that step 850, which I discarded initially because of its tendency towards darker hair tonalities, is probably a better TI overall than step 500. If you are using the new version, you might want to add "blonde" to your prompt to ensure that's the way she appears on screen, but in most cases it won't be necessary. Do check both versions and compare! :)

850-step TI trained on a dataset of 20 images with my usual settings.

Curious about my work process? I have summarized it here.

Appreciate my work? My TIs are free, but you can always buy me a coffee. :)
